            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1680535188884-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1680535188884-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 150ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [250ml]<strong> </span>boiled water </strong>to the pan with the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and 1/2 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tsp]</span><strong> sugar</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for 3-4 min or until the sauce has slightly thickened – this is your <strong>asparagus & tomato sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1680535199274-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1680535199274-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1680535199274-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1680535199274-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1680535199274-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>gnocchi </strong>and<strong> trimmed asparagus tips </strong>to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the gnocchi and asparagus for 3 min or until it begins to rise to the top of the pot and once done, drain both, reserving a cup of the<strong> starchy cooking water</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>cooked gnocchi</strong> and<strong> asparagus tips</strong> to the sauce and mix it all together, add a little <strong>starchy pasta water</strong> if your sauce is looking a little dry – this is your <strong>asparagus & tomato gnocchi</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1680535219818-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
